						<h3>
							<a href="//reason.com/reasontv/2017/05/03/kratom-drugs-opioid-epidemic-leaf-faith">'Kratom Is the Cure for the Opioid Epidemic.' Q&amp;A With Filmmaker Chris Bell</a>
